                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Charleston</placeName>\n                <date>21<hi rend=\"sup\">st</hi>. May 1843</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Knowing the deep interest<lb/> you manifest in every thing\n                appertaining to our<lb/> people I have selected this opportunity\n                <del>o</del>for<lb/> giving you an outline of the causes which<lb/> lend to the\n                present excitement and anarchy<lb/> in our congregation. While I deeply deplore<lb/>\n                the circumstances which have lead to the above results I cannot but\n                    <sic>beleive</sic> that the final<lb/> result will be beneficial, and will tend\n                towards<lb/> showing to the world that if a few zealous<lb/> &amp; perhaps well\n                meaning men rashly break down<lb/> the essentials which support our Holy\n                Religion<lb/> there are those (and many of them) who will cling to<lb/> it the more\n                closely the greater the attempts to<lb/> innovate &amp; reform it. You cannot reform\n                the<lb/> Jewish Religion—it is an absurdity. There<lb/> are but two Religions taught\n                in the Bible<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Judaism</hi> &amp; <hi rend=\"underline\">Christianity</hi> if\n                you break down<lb/> the <hi rend=\"underline\">fences</hi> which support the former\n                &amp;<lb/> which were built up by an almighty arm<lb/> you must necessarily enter\n                upon <sic>christian</sic><lb/> Ground. Every unbiased &amp; reflecting mind<lb/>\n                will acknowledge this a just conclusion.<lb/> But I <sic>shant</sic> tire your\n                patience with any</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3g15tx51/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
